parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the LCD screen can cause the control of various features, such as the radio, air conditioning, navigation, and backup camera, to become dysfunctional, leading to distractions while driving and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The screen will randomly beep
change air temperatures
start navigation
cause the loss of hands-free communication
and may even attempt to call emergency services. The screen may also display distorted views or bold colored lines
making it difficult to use the backup camera.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning backup camera can cause reduced visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The backup camera screen may display distorted views
bold colored lines
or may not display an image at all
making it difficult to see behind the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the LCD screen can cause the control of the radio, air conditioning, navigation, and other features to become dysfunctional, leading to driver distraction and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The screen will randomly beep
change air temperatures
start navigation
cause the loss of hands-free communication
and dial random numbers. The navigation system may become unreliable
and the screen may display incorrect information.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The trunk opening randomly while driving can cause a safety hazard, especially if the driver is distracted or loses control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The trunk will open on its own
even while driving
and may not close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause a safety hazard, especially if the driver is startled or loses control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The sunroof will suddenly shatter or explode
leaving a hole in the roof.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Blind Spot Monitoring System can cause a safety hazard, especially if the driver is not aware of vehicles in their blind spot.
symptoms: The system will not alert the driver of vehicles in their blind spot
or will alert them too late to prevent an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping can cause a safety hazard, especially if the driver loses control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The transmission will slip or hesitate
especially in low gears
and may cause the vehicle to jerk or lurch forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The door panels popping up can cause a safety hazard, especially if the driver is distracted or loses control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The door panels will suddenly pop up
even while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission problems can cause the vehicle to jerk, surge, or hesitate, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or surges when shifting gears
hesitates to accelerate
has difficulty shifting into gear
or makes grinding or howling noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical faults can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle's computer screen jumps around
changes settings randomly
blanks out
or beeps non-stop; the vehicle stalls or shuts down without warning; the parking brake engages unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission module can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the transmission module is faulty
the vehicle stalls or shuts down without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The infotainment system issues can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The LCD display becomes delaminated
display settings won't stay set
jumps around
beeps non-stop
loses saved settings
changes radio/SiriusXM stations randomly
changes climate control settings randomly.
